t that science is complicated and people who have scientific knowledge can make less money than those who are expertise in other areas resulting in less popularity in learning about science for university students moreover with the rise in this problem this trend possibly suspends the creation of new innovation and deteriorate the current environmental issues which are two most crucial matters for society ,8.5
