ring the needed knowledge within the current generation successfully these questions trigger that easier language to use doesn t neccessarily mean better documents but rather massive irrelevant amount of expolited work to summarive i tend to be of the opinion that the disadvantages outweigh the advantages of using a less formal language in writing the long term perspective could be significantly critisized as only short sighted point of views shall think that such methodology of written language helps human civilizations thrive in any way ,6.5
