m they can do so at home using the popular learning sites it doesnt necessarily have to be introduced into the school learning system in conclusion computers are currently the foundation of the modern world and have their advantages and disadvantages if they are put to the right use at the appropriate place and time its benefits are beyond measure ,7.5
