1,"The diagram below shows how solar panels can be used to provide electricity for domestic use.Write a report for a university, lecturer describing the information shown below.",the diagram illustrates the way how solar energy can be used as a source of household energy overall the process consists of 5 stages which implies the use of different devices namely solar panels the inverter the electrical panel the utility meter and the utility grid the construction needs the sunlight to be converted into energy afterwards first of all solar panels on the roof of the house absorb the sun energy and transform it into dc current next the dc current is converted into the ac current by going through an inverter which can also be used as the generated electricity controller it is important to note that the electrical panel is used in several ways first it distributes the electricity to your home second it is connected to the utility meter that flows back extra solar energy to the grid last but not least if the amount of sunshine is not enough to supply the house with electricity the utility grid that is also wired to the panel provides it in the usual way ,8.0
