thing else as a reward i g a free trip to somewhere a couple of coupon vouchers or even a car or house i would still be ungrateful compared with the extra money earned every month the reason is simply because stable income is considered more reliable than any other tangible or intagible assets in the perspective of an employee on top of that the incentives and bonus can be increased yearly or quaterly based on the company performance in summary i would like to reiterate that i agree on rewarding the emplyees with incentives and bonuses due to the fact that they can be as tool to build a strong montivation among the employees and deliver the company s gratitude toward them in an appropriate way ,5.0
