alia who asked the woman empoyees to always wear the skirt just after several strikes they obtained the permit to wear also pants on the other hand there are organisations in which how employees are dressed does not matter at all they believe the skills possessed by the workers go beyond a particular pair of shoes to take another example the skills of an employee have nothing to do with the color of her hair places like this consider a point of streengh the emotional and personal attitudes of the workers as well as they strongly believe that to show personal attitudes in a work context can give a major value to the work itself then they decide to leave free people to dress as they want without any restriction in conclusion i believe that the tendency to rule the way in which people should be dressed in the work place must be operated with high awarness the ceo of an agency can propose an office syle without compromise the particular attitudes and feelings of the employees ,6.0
