verything should be in the hands of the government they also feel that since it was their initiative to get that building built they should have the final say on how it should look like when it comes to my opinion i believe that the control of the design of the building should go to the person people who first thought of getting it constructed meaning the people hired architects and did the needful to get an ideal design of the building they want to construct ,6.5
