ate our carbon footprint therefore if humans shift to renewable and recyclable materials then it would drastically minimise the temperature rising issues to conclude people s actions that change the environment have a negative impact on the global climate however we can substantially lessen it by curbing fossil fuels and plastic usage ,8.0
