ment can also be seen today with many governments committing to proportions of their power needs coming from renewable resources i therefore strongly agree with the statement that the changes from reducing reliance on fossil fuels will be positive the only caveat is that society will need to have developed alternative sources of power rather soon in order to avoid an energy crisis ,9.0
