e to find them in addition if only a few books in print are available in the future libraries might be one of the few places where they might be accessed another purpose that libraries serve is acting as community centres that organise events education and childcare ironically libraries also provide computers and internet access for people who cannot afford their own in spite of the seeming dominance to come of digital books i feel that there is and will be a place for libraries with print books this state of affairs might change in the future but at present they are important community resources ,9.0
