wn the list of preferences of young audience and it takes a significant commitment from parents and teachers to ensure that children continue to read books to sum up modern technology can be a friend or a foe for young children depending on the choices adults in their lives make regulating the amount of screen time and its purpose without due care the writing and reading abilities of kids can be harmed by other more enjoyable activities they can use the devices for ,8.0
