e to work for their residents and negatively affects their quality of life in conclusion high rise and low rise buildings have their unique advantages and disadvantages in my opinion high rises are more suitable for younger residents and should be built in the areas where young population is prevalent closer to the city centre and employment opportunities senior citizens should have a supply of lower dwellings available in quieter locations such flexible approach can be a good way to address the needs of growing city s population ,8.0
