g their children close through adulthood parents should prepare in advance and raise their children to distinguish between right and wrong and teach them to take responsibility for their actions in conclusion although there might be some adverse consequences to this relatively new practice i believe that the advantages of young people leaving family home outweigh its drawbacks for both children and parents ,8.0
