 arguments are relevant and well developed there are only 2 body paragraphs but they are coherent and help to organise the information linking words are used appropriately to sequence ideas skillful use of synonyms throughout the essay demonstrates the writer s vocabulary some of the expressions used aren t entirely suitable or accurate but there aren t many of them overall this essay seems worthy of ielts band 8 0 ,8.0
