however in my opinion the government s involvement is essential to change the negative attitude by citing various advantages of international tourism to their country and raising awareness among tourists in order to protect local habitats this essay covers the entire task topic by exploring both reasons for negative attitude towards international tourism and some possible actions to change it the writer explains why locals may resent international tourists and suggests what steps can be taken to transform the way people feel about foreigners in their country the information is well organised by the use of paragraphing and the writer moves from one idea to the next effortlessly with the help of linking words a wide range of vocabulary is used including less common words such as degradation inhospitable habitat awareness and sacred instances of inaccurate word choice are rare and even these slips don t cause difficulty for the reader overall this looks like a band 8 essay ,8.0
