ng this is a great essay it addresses the two sides of the argument by exploring reasons why animals should and should not be used in medical research the ideas are well explained and supported by examples the use of paragraphing is efficient and helps with logical sequencing of ideas linking words are used appropriately to achieve the necessary cohesion author s meaning is skillfully conveyed by the use of wide range of vocabulary even though there are some inaccurately used expressions they don t hinder understanding most sentences are error free instances of faulty grammar are rare overall this essay seems worthy of ielts band 8 ,8.0
